:29:06.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"8a39e749ff11530c0b3f259470555831375eae82","tid":1760042,"uid":144492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T03:29:37.000Z","msg":"一開始講哂最嚴厲措辭<br />\n而家講嚟講去都發唔到圍<br />\n點算"},{"pid":"3066ebe7557f6d319946a19f0346341c04bcd19d","tid":1760042,"uid":44358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T03:30:12.000Z","msg":"中蟈幾時整個《紐約人權及民主法案》反制<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce1320801a123fddced3359f5d3d64c89be985f3","tid":1760042,"uid":135980,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T03:31:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3KnCudh.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3KnCudh.gif&h=2db79f75&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"88604ce908cb59982a1fa39968a246e277bc6359","tid":1760042,"uid":321041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T03:31:51.000Z","msg":"後果自負！後果自負！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6983164d173486f809c21749ac4f23971919200","tid":1760042,"uid":71428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T03:32:58.000Z","msg":"侵侵尊重甴<br />\n外交部即係唔尊重甴啦?"},{"pid":"14a6b773b0849dd58a3a81c3dbd25915c1a0db6b","tid":1760042,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T03:35:06.000Z","msg":"人地內政你咪理啦 唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95733bbf241ead6e340f50ab8e05593ea8b9c6a6","tid":1760042,"uid":290694,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T03:35:45.000Z","msg":"眼見連登一邊話立法會無可能過半, 立法會廢, 無用。我明。<br />\n<br />\n但係老豆豆講真係會有和理非, 會想係個制度裡面盡可能改變令普遍市民既聲音可以主導個政府。<br />\n<br />\n我亦都知好大部分人係堅信五大訴求，缺一不可。<br />\n首先係要政府回應、答應五大訴求先。<br />\n其中一項係真雙普選，如果做唔到依樣野，係唔可以一步到位做到從體制裡面改變香港。<br />\n但係淋病政府一直冷處理，一路拖，拖左我地半年依家先出個&lt;&lt;獨立&quot;檢討&quot;委員會&gt;&gt;。<br />\n<br />\n我個人無咁叻，我唔知道政府黎緊會點做。<br />\n我唔知個政府想拖我地幾耐。<br />\n政府唔回應、答應。我地就升級再升級。<br />\n就好似打緊一場長久而睇唔到終點既仗。<br />\n<br />\n但係立法會選舉下年黎緊，話長唔長，話短唔短，好快就到！<br />\n我地仲係到自己人屌自己人，做人都要有Plan A，Plan B。<br />\n點解仲唔可以停止爭論！<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求我地要政府俾到交代我地，缺一不可。<br />\n立法會最基本野要做好，夠資格就登記做選民。<br />\n兄弟爬山，各自努力，目標一致。<br />\n繼續high人權法、區議會，我睇唔到香港人出路！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n推下行動post好過啦!!!"},{"pid":"1a23ce7a7deaf034d9790abc353ed59964891a06","tid":1760042,"uid":28168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T03:35:47.000Z","msg":"反了反了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8c5e2a5dc0b484eeb4b5d8cdfa345cb76c6d2dc","tid":1760042,"uid":144529,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T03:36:29.000Z","msg":"我比較想知強國有咩反制"},{"pid":"b0d53e696e3ccc03eb19f5a23c0770506011733d","tid":1760042,"uid":3508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T03:36:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yDGytnn.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyDGytnn.gif&h=6a977dfc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb160feccf30f04d8273728b76d2878d091a6cb8","tid":1760042,"uid":261332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T03:37:43.000Z","msg":"反制咗兩年喇wor，仲慢過流浮山刀手。"},{"pid":"885c4d280c4abb9a188bb9b0262fc1d8c99bbd8f","tid":1760042,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3066ebe7557f6d319946a19f0346341c04bcd19d","tid":1760042,"uid":44358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T03:30:12.000Z","msg":"中蟈幾時整個《紐約人權及民主法案》反制<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T03:39:34.000Z","msg":"習明澤點算，葉劉屋企人點算？"},{"pid":"ca0db47c09202accc3d814373e5261529592a24a","tid":1760042,"uid":196450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T03:39:45.000Z","msg":"其實中國口交部同香港啲鍵戰一鳩樣 得把口網上嬲完實際乜都做唔到"}]}